^5Help - Ewizcast
~5USAGE: .ewizcast ^5message
~5WHERE: ^message ~5is something you wish to emote to other wizards

~5Use this command when you want to emote a message to only the Wizards and
~5Gods that are online.  By itself, it will review the last several
~5wizcasts and emoted wizcasts.

~5EXAMPLES
  ~5.ewizcast
  ~5.ewizcast smiles.

~5SEE ALSO
  ^5.help wizcast

